# 📰 News Aggregator

**News Aggregator** is a modern web app that delivers **trending news** from multiple sources in real-time.  
Users can **browse by category, search for specific topics, and bookmark their favorite articles** for later reading — all in one clean, responsive interface.

---

## ✨ Features
- 🚀 **Trending News Feed** — Always stay updated with the hottest headlines.
- 🌍 **Multiple News Sources** — Aggregates from top publishers & APIs.
- 🗂 **Category Filtering** — Browse by Business, Sports, Technology, Entertainment, and more.
- 🔍 **Keyword Search** — Find stories about any topic instantly.
- 📌 **Bookmark Articles** — Save your favorite news to read later.
- 🕒 **Real-Time Updates** — Fresh content every time you open the app.
- 📱 **Responsive Design** — Works perfectly on desktop, tablet, and mobile.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack
### **Frontend**
- ⚛️ React.js
- 🎨 Tailwind CSS
- 🔄 Axios (API calls)
- 📂 Local Storage (for bookmarks)

### **Backend**
- 🟢 Node.js
- 🚂 Express.js
- 📰 News API (gnews api)
- 🗃 MongoDB 

---

